body:
Request for "coarse flatten" to remove "module level" connections.
```
module top ( a, b, yy );
   input [1:0] a,b;
   output yy;
wire y1, y2;

redu_test redu_a (
.a (a), 
.b (b), 
.y (y1)
);

redu_test redu_b (
.a (a), 
.b (b), 
.y (y2)
);

assign yy = y1 & y2;

endmodule

module redu_test ( a, b, y );
   input [1:0] a,b;
   output y;
   assign y = |{(a == b)};
endmodule
```
```
read_verilog redu_test.v 
proc
hierarchy -top top
flatten
write_verilog koe.v
```

